{"title":"About","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"About","image":"profile.jpg","about":{"template":"jolla","links":[{"icon":"twitter","text":"Twitter","href":"https://twitter.com"},{"icon":"linkedin","text":"LinkedIn","href":"https://linkedin.com"},{"icon":"github","text":"Github","href":"https://github.com"}]}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n我仰卧在时光中，等待我一直在等待的东西。\n\n我特别敬爱纪晓岚，或许是受到了电视剧《铁齿铜牙纪晓岚》的影响，虽然不是史实，里面纪晓岚的形象还是给我留下很深的触动。\n\n我也曾以纪晓岚为目标，希望自己成为他那样的大才子。结果还是事与愿违。\n\n就起一个“山寨”版的名字吧。自己为李姓——索性就叫……铜牙铁岚李小嘴吧。\n\n不知道从什么时候开始，我想整一个公众号，不是玩票，也不是心血来潮，只是想找个地方，自己说自己的话，自己侃自己的所过的生活，自己聊自己所玩儿的游戏。\n\n1986，我降生在一个平凡却很幸福的家庭。到今天，已经有33年了。\n\n我从来不认为自己是一个有故事的人，至少，现在不是。每当我回忆过去的时候，脑海中浮现出的只是底片，却没有连起来。我向他们可以连起来，连贯成一部电影而不仅仅只是一张无声的照片。这是个愿望，我尝试在这里将他实现。\n\n我把这个叫做的我的回忆，也是我一直在等待的东西。"},"formats":{"html":{"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-yaml":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[]},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","css":["styles.css"],"output-file":"about.html"},"language":{},"metadata":{"lang":"en","fig-responsive":tru